			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				There are way too many pros for Iksar shammies to put them out of this. IKSARS have the highest base wisdom, not Barbarians, they have regen, infravision, and pretty well-rounded stats (on par with humans). They also have 4 of the BEST starting areas in the game.  Lake of Ill Omens will take you from level 2 to level 30 or so. Also, they have great quests to do for upgradeable weapons (the beginner weapon is excellent as it is, something like 6-8/26). People should take more time to examine the Iksar and try them out. Its well worth being evil (which you can change)!
				</font>
